##After the outbreak, we decided to solve the problem of "mask face" and "alcohol hand" 

Micro Signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

So far, Jialan has donated more than 10 million yuan, the country's nearly 20,000 health care workers have used Jialan products, we are very proud to be able to do something for the first-line health care workers.

Dictation | Chen Juanling

Sorting out | Shen Lin

For more than a month now, every day from morning to night in the busy, dealing with the epidemic in the company's internal and external communication, for a long time did not sleep a complete.

I'm Chen Juanling, general manager of Public Relations and communication of Galan Group. You may be familiar with our cosmetics brands, such as Naturelle, Meisu, Chunxia, plant intelligence, purveyor, Como, etc. . Although we can not, like the angels in White, go directly to the front line to save lives, every day since the outbreak of the disease, from the group chairman Mr. Zheng Chunying to the management team has been thinking, as China's leading cosmetics company, what can we do to fulfill more responsibilities and responsibilities.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Back on January 20, we saw the news that there was human to human transmission of COVID-19 pneumonia in Wuhan, experts advised everyone to wear a mask. Because the company began the Spring Festival holiday on January 22, so the first time the purchase of 1000 KN95 masks, issued to colleagues who returned home in the New Year. At the same time, we have also placed an order of 2 million yuan from the mask factory to donate to the front line of the epidemic, as well as our employees and their families, as well as our partners.

Unexpectedly, two days later, the manufacturer told us that the mask factory had been requisitioned by the government. After hearing the news, we fully understand and support it. We also thought that it must be difficult to purchase medical supplies at home. So we urgently contacted our colleagues overseas to help coordinate and do global procurement. On January 23, the company also set up a "galant epidemic prevention and Control Emergency Response Team" , requiring all employees to update their health status on a daily basis, and to purchase effective drugs from overseas as a reserve for employees in need.

Our professional efficacy skin care brand poffyan and the hospital is very close contact. On January 25(the first day of the Lunar New Year) , when news of COVID-19 pneumonia in Wuhan became more and more popular, especially the severe shortage of materials in the Wuhan Union Hospital, we immediately responded by donating 2,000 masks, directly to the hospital, also sent 1,000 masks to the company's Hubei Line of beauty consultants staff, although a small number, but have done their best.

On January 28, the situation of epidemic prevention and control became more and more serious. We urgently coordinated with the official designated organization, the Wuhan Red Cross Society, and donated 5 million yuan in cash in the hope of making a contribution to the fight against the epidemic.

With the outbreak, the group learned that some local hospitals in Shanghai are also in short supply, so donated 5,000 KN95 masks to Shanghai Ruijin Hospital. In addition, Sangharama donated 3,000 masks to Jinhui and Situan towns in Fengxian district of Shanghai, in addition, 1,200 Pfeken 728 creams and 3,000 nature hall hand creams have been donated to 600 first-line health care workers in the Fengxian District district, including admission points, fever clinics in hospitals, community isolation points, etc. , send 2,000 KN95 masks and 200 bottles of pofoken 728 cream to Wuhan and other first-line Logistics Support Personnel.

We also noticed that wearing masks for a long time caused doctors and nurses to assume that wearing masks for a long time would keep the skin hot and breathless, and would be easy to breed bacteria, also easy to make the cheeks, nose Alar, after the ear occurs pressure damage, and some mask fabric will produce some free Formaldehyde, leading to skin allergy.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The soothing ingredients of Pofoyan 728 cream, Tibetan hot spring water and purslane, can effectively relieve the skin's allergic reaction and improve the facial itching, redness and other discomfort caused by the sensitization of the mask. The product also added a deep moisturizing ingredients shea butter, to prevent the mask parts of the skin after evaporation dry scaling. We thought, isn't this the skin sensitivity that purveyor 728 is best at solving?

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
As a result, since February 1, the pofoken brand has donated products from all over the world to 144 hospitals and 3 medical teams in 26 provinces, and donated a total of about 3.31 million yuan worth of pofoken 728 cream, to alleviate the "mask face" problem of 12608 personnel. Later, the People's Daily also discovered the phenomenon of "face mask" and specially posted a set of wechat photo news called "face" , which attracted wide attention from everyone, as a result, more skin care brands for medical staff "mask face" began to join the ranks of caring donations.

On Feb. 9, we were concerned that staff at Wuhan Hankou Hospital posted a request for help on Weibo, saying that the hospital's young nurses were in urgent need of hand cream. Originally, because daily frequent use of disinfectant, hand lotion, fighting in the first line of the white angels hand Eczema, peeling, chapped and so on.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
After seeing the news, we were very distressed. The next day, we asked our colleagues in Wuhan to contact the hospital and transfer all the 5,000 hand creams from the natural hall and the Spring and summer brands in the entire Wuhan area together, was taken to Hankou Hospital by Sangharama's staff. Natural hand cream contains precious rose hip oil ingredients, Spring and summer hand cream contains shea butter ingredients, can effectively help medical staff to deal with the "alcohol hand" this phenomenon.

At the same time, we also sent more than twenty-five thousand hand creams from the warehouse in Shanghai to Hankou Hospital in Wuhan, Jinyintan Hospital, Yiling District hospital, Yichang Central Hospital, Yichang First People's hospital, tongji Hospital, People's Hospital of Peking University medical team, Shanghai Medical Aid Hubei team.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
These things are actually quite ordinary. We did our best. Later, after CCTV news broadcast and the news studio reported our Charity Action Successively, the company received many requests for help from different channels, we are also aware that more and more places need these materials, so the follow-up has also connected more medical teams and anti-epidemic front-line staff to make "mask face" , "alcohol hand" donations.

At the same time, in response to the call of the state and the government, we have postponed the original resumption of work from February 3 to February 10. The return rate and the return rate on the opening day of the factory are low, because many workers returning to Shanghai from other places have to stay at home for 14 days, so in order to increase production capacity, we have also thought of a number of ways, including the "shared staff" program.

Galan's factory is located in Fengxian, Shanghai. We are also a representative enterprise of Oriental Meigu, so after we have applied to the District Party Committee and District government for the requirement, the district's first response has helped us coordinate other catering and pension companies in the park to come to work in our factory. We are very happy that different industries keep each other warm during hard times.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On February 12,24 catering staff of Galan factory received "reinforcement" , (all have not left Shanghai or have completed 14 days isolation period) after training as workshop operators, salary by Galan Bear. "reinforcement" to allow us to expand from the original 2 production lines to 4 production lines, the first week back to work capacity increased by 28% . But in the limited personnel, we are also focused on the most needed products, mainly to do Pfeken 728 cream and hand cream production. In the recent past, a second group of shared employees has also arrived, and we have partnered with a nursing home to hire its nursing staff to work in our production line and logistics positions, bringing the total number of shared employees to 119.

In addition, we judge that during the epidemic, the community for disinfection and sterilization products demand will become very large. As a matter of fact, experts in the news reports suggest that you do a good job of disinfection and sterilization work, related to some of the ingredients such as alcohol disinfection and hand sanitizer, in some areas there is a shortage of products out of stock. Therefore, we have decided to quickly put into production 10 products of "disinfectant" , "hand sanitizer without washing" and "sanitary towel" under three brands of Naturehall, Chunxia and Pufuyan, to meet the rigid demand of consumers, to relieve social pressure.

Sangharama has been working on anti virus products, but the arrival of the epidemic has accelerated the launch of new products. In order to products can quickly on-line, we also with production partners to do a good job of coordination, and strive to the shortest time to be able to put into production.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Adding new businesses is also a way for our business to weather the storm. SANGHARAMA's 19 year history includes SARS in 2003, financial crises in 2008 and 2012, but we all survived, and this one will have an economic impact, but we're going to do our best to treat it as if it were always going to be a great product and service, and that's why we've created this emergency.

Gallant's killing products will be on the market by the end of February. As a leading local cosmetics company in China, Sangharama was not able to act as a doctor or a nurse in the first line of care for the patients during the nearly one month of the epidemic, but every day we actively organized the resumption of work and production, trying to find a way to contribute to the fight and supply of this epidemic, all in the same boat, pay tribute to all "the most beautiful retrograde people" !
